Package edu.odu.cs.cs350

Class Website

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.odu.cs.cs350.Website
  • public class Website
extends java.lang.Object
    Website holds a collection of all files in the target directory, as well as a collection of all HtmlDocuments. Also invokes output writers.
